881.title: Count of Monte Cristo (Version 4 Dramatic Reading)
881.description: The Count of Monte Cristo is one of the authors most popular works. It's an adventure novel that takes place between 1815-1838 in France, Italy, islands in the Mediterranean and in the Levant. It follows the main character through love, betrayal, vengence and forgiveness.  Summary by Kristingj
